Version 2.0

- Add 2 new glass doors
- Changed a few textures
- Add a new monster
- New custom props
- More glass break this time




Huge Labyrinth created by the government to test the inteligence of aliens and zombies.
If you are an human run to the control room and save your ass, because there's no hope inside the laby.
If you are outside the control room, you're dead, budy.

I hope you guys enjoy this map.
A lot of work and more in the future.

Set the time to 7:00 min per round
The control is locked by pressing the button in the red painel.

Enjoy and give me some feedback.
